org.afplib.afplib

Interface ObjectOffset

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, Triplet
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ObjectOffsetImpl

    public interface ObjectOffset
extends Triplet
    A representation of the model object 'Object Offset'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Obj Tpe
    • Obj Oset
    • Obj Ost Hi

    See Also:
    AfplibPackage.getObjectOffset()
